2013年4月26日，CW電視網宣布《創始吸血鬼》為完整的一季<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/01/11/the-cw-orders-backdoor-pilot-for-vampire-diaries-spinoff-the-originals/165059/ |title=The CW Orders Backdoor Pilot for 'Vampire Diaries' Spinoff, 'The Originals' |first=Amanda |last=Kondolojy |work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |date=January 11, 2013 |accessdate=April 27, 2013 |archive-date=2013-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130120121301/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/01/11/the-cw-orders-backdoor-pilot-for-vampire-diaries-spinoff-the-originals/165059/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，也宣佈預定本劇於[[2013年－2014年美國電視網節目表|2013年－2014年]]播出<ref>{{cite web |author=Michael Ausiello |url=http://tvline.com/2013/04/26/the-cw-renewed-shows-list-2013-hart-of-dixie-beauty-and-the-beast/ |title=The CW Shows Renewed 2013 — ‘Hart of Dixie,’ ‘Beauty and the Beast’ |publisher=TVLine |date=2013-04-26 |accessdate=2013-04-27 |archive-date=2013-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502035555/http://tvline.com/2013/04/26/the-cw-renewed-shows-list-2013-hart-of-dixie-beauty-and-the-beast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個第二次的[[衍生劇|衍生劇]]嘗試將由茱莉·普雷克監督，而[[凱文·威廉森|凱文·威廉森]]則不會參與<ref>{{cite news |title='Vampire Diaries' Spinoff 'The Originals' in the Works at CW |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/vampire-diaries-spinoff-works-at-411487 |first=Lesley |last=Goldberg |author2=Philiana Ng |date=January 11, 2013 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=January 13, 2013 |archive-date=2013-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113001014/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/vampire-diaries-spinoff-works-at-411487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《創始吸血鬼》的第一季原本預定於10月15日星期二首播<ref>{{Cite web |title=The CW sets fall premieres: 'Tomorrow People,' 'The Originals' |date=June 24, 2013 |author=Tim Kenneally |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-us-cw-fallpremieresbre95n1cn-20130624,0,4682924.story |work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] |accessdate=2020-08-10 |archive-date=2013-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005065626/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-us-cw-fallpremieresbre95n1cn-20130624,0,4682924.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，2013年7月29日，CW又宣布將該系列首映改於2013年10月3日播出，繼《噬血Y世代》第五季首映之後，以吸引該系列的影迷<ref name="date change" />。2013年10月10日，CW電視網訂購了該系列的其他三個腳本<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2013/10/10/cw-the-originals-tomorrow-people-reign-additional-script-orders/ |title=The CW Orders Additional Scripts for ''The Originals'', ''Tomorrow People'' and ''Reign'' |work=TV Line |last=Gelman |first=Vlada |date=October 10, 2013 |accessdate=October 11, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010233152/http://tvline.com/2013/10/10/cw-the-originals-tomorrow-people-reign-additional-script-orders/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年11月11日，CW決定為《創始吸血鬼》訂購完整的一季<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cw-gives-full-season-orders-to-freshman-series-the-originals-the-tomorrow-people-reign/ |title=CW Gives Full-Season Orders To Freshman Series 'The Originals', 'The Tomorrow People' & 'Reign' |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |date=November 11, 2013 |accessdate=November 11, 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205203236/http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cw-gives-full-season-orders-to-freshman-series-the-originals-the-tomorrow-people-reign/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

